<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>Asti samastadigaṁtaraviśrāṁtaduraṁtakīrttivistāraḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> bāhābala<unclear>ji</unclear>tavairi<unclear>sa</unclear>mū
<lb n="2" break="no"/>haḥ ponnāḍakēsabhūpālaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> bhāginēyastasya vibhōruḍumayaprabhunaṁddanaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> yaṟṟāṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>bātanayō bhāti kūrmmēṁdrō bhāvayānujaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> śākē vēdakarābdhibhūparimitē saṁvatsarē
<lb n="4"/>durmatau māsē phālguṇanāmni paṁccamadinē pakṣē sitedasrabhē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> prākāraṁ parigṛhya nū
<lb n="5" break="no"/>tnaghaṭitaṁ ponā ḍakūrmaprabhuṁ taṁ pāyādanugṛhya sarpanagarē śrībhāvanā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rāyaṇaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">4</supplied> svasti śrīśakavarṣaṁbulu 1<unclear>4</unclear>24 Agunēṁṭi du<unclear>rmma</unclear>tisaṁvvatsara phālgu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>na śu 5 ku mahāmahimagala pānnāḍa<unclear>dharmma</unclear>rājā[nu Arjunasamānulaina] kēsayama
<lb n="8" break="no"/>hāpātṛlaku mēnalluṁḍaina kūrmayamahapātruṁḍu tama taṁḍri Uḍumayyaṁgā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>rikinni tama talli yaṟṟamāṁbakunnu tama tōḍaṁbuṭṭina <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> dēvamahāpātṛla
<lb n="10" break="no"/>kunnu puṇyamavunaṭṭugānu sarppavarapu śrībhāvanārāyaṇadēvuni tiracuṭṭumālā
<lb n="11"/>Ādimūlaṁguḍi gōpāḷa dēvuḷaṁ naḍumu krottagānu Āyittaṁ cēyiṁci Ācaṁdrā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>rkasthāyigānu samarpaṇacēsenu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> maṁgaḷamahāśrīśrīṁ jēyunu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> plabhattuni vīraya vrālu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

